title: Evans Blue - The Stage is Set for the Revival of an Anthem
description:
This is Evans Blue's "unofficial" third album. Released in August 2008 by Kevin Matisyn on his PureVolume account, these songs were meant to be on their third album "The Stage is Set for the Revival of an Anthem". Some of these songs are full studio quality, while some are obviously just demos.

I've included the 12 album tracks as well as the 3 B-Side tracks.

1. Burn
2. Right Now
3. Gone Again
4. On My Own
5. Out There
6. Good Enough
7. The Main Attraction at Our Recovery
8. Into the Sun
9. No One Looks as Good as You in That
10. This Stare
11. An Anthem
12. Look

B1. Michelle's Song
B2. Jean's Song
B3. The Good Times


Enjoy this wonderful album!
